Consider what&#39;s going on.  You said `hanoi 4 ...` and the next line of code of any significance is `hanoi (4 - 1) ...` which, as @user2407038 has already commented, is going to be followed by `hanoi 2`, `hanoi 1` and `hanoi 0`.

